title: Photo Technique - Autumn 2013  UK
description:
Photo Technique - Autumn 2013  UK

English | 140 Pages | True PDF | 55 MB 


Photo Technique is a photography magazine like non other offering quality portfolios by leading photographers from around the world, in all fields and applications of photography. Accompanying articles explain the reasoning, technology and methodology used in the execution of the works. Also included in each issue are extended, in-depth technical articles-not just tips, but full descriptions of photographic processes and techniques, commentary by leading visionaries in the field of photography who discuss the issues confronting an ever-expanding medium, and innovative products that will improve your workflow and your photographs.
